OL,3,CUK inflation remains steady for May,
OL,4,Cagainst expectations
OL,6,FUK inflation remained unchanged at
OL,7,F2.8% in May, the Office for National
OL,8,FStatistics (ONS) has said.
OL,10,FThe ONS said higher airfares and fuel
OL,11,Fprices were offset by lower food
OL,12,Fprices.
OL,14,FExperts had predicted a slight rise in
OL,15,Finflation for last month.
OL,17,FThe Consumer Price Index (CPI)
OL,18,Finflation had slowed to its lowest
OL,19,Flevel in more than a year in April,
OL,20,Fdue to a decline in household energy
OL,21,Fprices for the month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
