OL,3,CUK inflation remains steady for May,
OL,4,Cagainst expectations
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBank of England forecasts from April
OL,12,Fpredicted that inflation would average
OL,13,Faround 3.1% in the second quarter of
OL,14,Fthis year and peak at around 3.6% in a
OL,15,Fmore benign scenario related to the
OL,16,FMiddle East conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
