OL,3,CUK inflation remains steady for May,
OL,4,Cagainst expectations
OL,6,FOn Thursday, policymakers at the
OL,7,Fcentral bank will vote on whether to
OL,8,Fmaintain interest rates at their
OL,9,Fcurrent rate of 3.75% or increase or
OL,10,Fdecrease this rate.
OL,12,FThe Bank is expected to hold off on an
OL,13,Finterest rate hike, despite concerns
OL,14,Fthat the Middle East conflict will
OL,15,Fpush the cost of living higher.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
